<title>UK: RESEARCH ALERT-Akzo Nobel upped to &quot;buy&quot;.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Akzo Nobel upped to &quot;buy&quot;.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-08-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Chemical group Akzo Nobel was upgraded to  a &quot;buy&quot; rating from &quot;hold&quot; at CSFB, the investment bank said on Friday.   </p>
<p>Akzo Nobel's 25 percent rise in second-quarter earnings announced  on Thursday, confirmed &quot;the group is back on the growth track, with  strong underlying sales growth and solid margin improvements across  all the key areas,&quot; analysts at CSFB said.</p>
<p>CSFB raised its price target to 402 guilders. Shares were trading  up 14.50 at 335.30 at1038 GMT.</p>
<p>-- John Hanley, London Newsroom +44 171 542 4366</p>
